snippet.title: Bagheera Kannada Official Trailer | Sriimurali & Rukmini | Dr Suri | Prashanth Neel | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
ROAR WITH EXCITEMENT!

Get ready for the ultimate action-packed ride! Watch the explosive trailer of #Bagheera, produced by Hombale Films, the makers of KGF, Kantara, and Salaar! 
Directed by Dr. Suri,  created by visionary director Prashanth Neel, Music by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and Produced by Vijay Kiragandur.

The countdown begins! Bagheera hits theaters on Oct 31st!

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. How to make perfect Besan Ladu Recipe | Halwai Style 1 kilo besan ladu recipe¬†

How to make Besan Laddu Flour -
 ‚Ä¢ Dry roast chana dal on very flame until they get light marks on it
 ‚Ä¢ Once done, allow the dal to comes at room temp & then take it to the flour mill for grinding
 ‚Ä¢ Make little coarse texture flour, which is perfect for laddus

How to make Besan laddu -
 ‚Ä¢ heat up some ghee into a kadhai, add besan & roast on low flame for 2-3 mins
 ‚Ä¢ then add some more besan & roast for 2 more mins, again add remaining besan & roast the besan on low flame until besan changes the color to light golden brown & get aromatic
 ‚Ä¢ While roasting the besan make sure to keep the flame low, roast continuously & break all the lumps from the besan
 ‚Ä¢ After 25 mins of roasting, if you find the besan is still dry then add some extra ghee
 ‚Ä¢ Once besan is roasted completely, sprinkle some water or milk & mix well for 2 mins & turn off the flame
 ‚Ä¢ Take the roasted besan to a parat or large plate & allow it to cool down
 ‚Ä¢ Once the roasted besan comes at room temp, add powder sugar & cardamom pw to it¬†
 ‚Ä¢ mix everything well, break sugar lumps if any & roll the laddus
 ‚Ä¢ Our delicious besan laddu is ready

How to make perfect Besan Ladu Recipe | Halwai Style 1 kilo besan ladu recipe¬†

How to make Besan Laddu Flour -
 ‚Ä¢ Dry roast chana dal on very flame until they get light marks on it
 ‚Ä¢ Once done, allow the dal to comes at room temp & then take it to the flour mill for grinding
 ‚Ä¢ Make little coarse texture flour, which is perfect for laddus

How to make Besan laddu -
 ‚Ä¢ heat up some ghee into a kadhai, add besan & roast on low flame for 2-3 mins
 ‚Ä¢ then add some more besan & roast for 2 more mins, again add remaining besan & roast the besan on low flame until besan changes the color to light golden brown & get aromatic
 ‚Ä¢ While roasting the besan make sure to keep the flame low, roast continuously & break all the lumps from the besan
 ‚Ä¢ After 25 mins of roasting, if you find the besan is still dry then add some extra ghee
 ‚Ä¢ Once besan is roasted completely, sprinkle some water or milk & mix well for 2 mins & turn off the flame
 ‚Ä¢ Take the roasted besan to a parat or large plate & allow it to cool down
 ‚Ä¢ Once the roasted besan comes at room temp, add powder sugar & cardamom pw to it¬†
 ‚Ä¢ mix everything well, break sugar lumps if any & roll the laddus
 ‚Ä¢ Our delicious besan laddu is ready

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Thozha - Back to Back comedy scene | Karthi | Nagarjuna | Vivek | Tammanah | Adithya TV
snippet.description:
The story revolves around Vikramadhitya (Nagarjuna) a quadriplegic billionaire, and Seenu, (Karthi) his ex-convict caretaker. Circumstances in their life teach them the value of relationships over money. 

Thozha is a 2016 movie . It was released in both Telugu and Tamil languages. Its name in Telugu is Oppri . The film is a remake of the French film The Intouchables . The film stars Karthik Sivakumar , Nagarsuna , Tamannaah , Prakasu Rasu , Vivek , Anushka , Seyashuda , Sireyya . The film is directed by Vamsi Baidipalli and produced by Prasad V Potluri.

snippet.description:

Lyrics

CHOWK - 99side 

Dikhna mat chowk par bhokte
Khule bazaar mein kholte
Nahin sochta kya bolte chaar log hain
Bana dete chaar kandhon ka bojh hai
Hum lakadbagghe seedha nochte
Muft mein gang de rahi moksh hai
Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte
Dikhna mat, dikhna mat
Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte
Khule Bazaar mein kholte thokte
Kidhar se bolte Vile ke chhokre
Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte
Dikhna mat dikhna mat
Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte
Dikhna mat dikhna mat
 Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte

Yerwada jail meri jaib kare Daandi ko qaid
Inhein sone ki na parakh tabhi chandi chunein
Tu chandi ka chammach mila bachpan se sab
Hum toofan kyunki janam diya aandhi ne hai
Hum bhakt hai Bhagat ke
khaulta rakht nass mein
Gulaami ke badle phaansi chunein
Mujhse jung matlab maafi kadaapi nahin
Lanka jalaa ke kardun tere naabi mein chhed
Banani mujhe Legacy jo hogi lambi Draupadi ke saree jaise
Likhta baareeki se bhaari paise chahiye shabdon ke
kyunki shabdon ka kaarigar main
Paison ke paudhon ko ugaate
hum mehnat paseene se
Hustle ye maali jaise
Jo bole paise se milti khushi nahin
Bol raha woh munh se nahi pichhwaade se hai
Dogle log ke thopde fode
Tu phuski bam hum Tope ke gole
Tu weak hai bahut hum potte Boss hai
Hum se lafde matlab khoon se lathpath,
Jaise bacche aate kokh se.
Bahaayega khoon galey milayegi maut
Bahaayega paseena kamaayega note
Kamaayega note to gawaayega apne

Waqt ke na saath par waqt badal doon
Tune chheena mera haqq tera takth badal doon 
Gaane likhe Maine saare sab qatal doon
Tu ne kare kaafi jhol khud se kar kuch
Zyaada bak mat chote mere haat ka mal tu
Bandana pehne par thug nahin hai tu
Dikhta na zyada main jaise full moon
Chhote cheel ki chonch hoon saanp leke udd loon
Dekhe tere jaise bane shaane
Peeth peeche bakey baatein
Mere baare tere baare mein
na thoda bhi sochun
Main karun joh bhi mann bole na ki baaki jann bole
Bhediyon ke bheed mein tu bakri ghonchu
Lage mere saare peeche, gulaabi note hoon
Girne waale ko utha doon aisi chot hoon
Vigyaan bhi na pahonche vigyaan bhi na soche main aisi khoj hoon

Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte
Dikhna mat, dikhna mat Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte
Khule Bazaar mein kholte
Nahin sochta kya bolte chaar log hai 
Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte
Dikhna mat , dikhna mat Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte
Khule Bazaar mein kholte thokte Kidhar se bolte Vile ke chokre
Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte
Dikhna mat dikhna mat Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte
Dikhna mat dikhna mat Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte
Vile Parle, Bambai sheher, 99side, Dikhna mat chowk pe Lala

Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte
Khule bazar mein kholte
Nahin sochta kya bolte chaar (4) log hai
Banaa dete chaar (4) kandhon ka bojh hai
Hum lakadbagghe seedha nochte
Muft mein gang de rahi moksh hai
Dikhna mat Chowk par bhokte bhokte Dikhna mat , dikhna mat 

Jali jali teri mere se jali toh phir jadibooti lagaake tu thandi kara le
Khade khade tujhe bata doon mere kalam mein kitni taakat jo ki teri garmi utaare
Fati padi teri tabhi jabhi likhi maine tere barein mein ye sabi sacchi jo baatein
Nahin bhoolunga woh raatein
Jo bhi bina khaana khaate
Bina sote likhe maine gaane
Jo bhi tere saath hai
sacche waade nahin nibhaate
Badi baatein par bahaane
Maine likhe sacche gaane
Hum karke dikhaate tum karte dikhaave
Mere baaton mein jo baat
Tere baaton mein na baat hai
Main baatein badhaa doon tere paas baatein karne ko na baat hai
Jo bhi saath mere khaas hai
Aata jahan se milte bas jhaanse
Tu nahin khaas hai
banta bas khaas hai
nikal na yahan se
Rehta main khud hi mein magan
Duniyadari se nahin hai lain dain
Funny dekh kitni yahan game hai
Saare rappers sound hote hain same same
Jo naak ghista khud
wahi dusron ko bolta hai shembde
Alien rapperon ke liye bhai tera Ben-10

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Jaan Nisar Episode 64 Teaser - 19th October 2024 - Har Pal Geo

7th Sky Entertainment‚Äôs mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan
Ghaznavi‚Äôs love?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Director: Mohsin Mirza
Writer: Rehana Aftab

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. snippet.title: EXCLUSIVE: MOHD SHAMI ON HIS IPL RETENTION WITH GUJARAT TITANS AND COMEBACK PLANS FOR AUSTRALIA TOUR
snippet.description:
In an exclusive interview with Sports Tak fast bowler Mohammed Shami has proclaimed that he is fully fit and is aiming a comeback in the Border Gavaskar Trophy against Australia. Shami, who has not played a competitive game since ODI World Cup 2023, said that he wants to play a couple of Ranji Trophy games to get match-fit.

The pacer has been at the National Cricket Academy since his ankle surgery after the World Cup, and has been rehabilitating under the watchful eyes of the Board of Control for Cricket in India medical staff. Shami was recently seen bowling with a strapped knee at the centre wicket after the Bengaluru Test match.
